Mi1hMmQ5LTk1YWFjZGExZDIxMSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAYzN75DqK_UE-Fj-mAqjeeppLGwS2Z9RpDKbrmZItdRB&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08N5LNQCX%2F">苹果 M1 MacBook Air</a>重新以 800 美元的价格出售，这是我们之前多次看到的促销价格，但追平了笔记本电脑的历史最低价。与第 9 代 iPad 一样，M1 MacBook Air 现在也比较老旧。如果您能买得起具有更新设计、更好的网络摄像头和更快的 M2 芯片的<a data-i13n="cpos:52;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIzQ0RaTFRCP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE0YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzkxN2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAYTS19Nj8nFE-hvAuFQKiayEVgr1SXMSBzeIjNM8i1hW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B3CDZLTB">最新 Air</a> ，那么这是<a data-i13n="cpos:53;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/macbook-air-m2-review-2022-130040098.html">值得的</a>。但如果你只是想要一台功能强大的 MacBook 以尽可能少的现金进行轻松的工作和网页浏览，那么 M1 Air 在这个价格上仍然具有坚实的价值。它的键盘、触控板和电池续航时间仍然非常出色，而且 M1 芯片的速度仍然足以满足必需品的需求。不过，请确保您坚持较轻的工作负载，因为该型号只有 8GB RAM 和 256GB SSD。</p><h2>苹果 MacBook Pro 14 英寸</h2><p><core-commerce id="bdeda2f11cd449a08cf36083b4a2d409" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>对于那些有更苛刻需求的人来说，配备 M2 Pro 芯片、16GB RAM 和 1TB SSD 的<a data-i13n="cpos:54;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVQIh3DiEUuJzj2LhC5mDvoYYX4tfFsQseyGapjxJo1d&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BSHDT7F5%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1">14 英寸 MacBook Pro</a>在<a data-i13n="cpos:55;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https:/