N2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAR67s_ZXpseJDSY9mPaaUFAdEEADR5DZmtpR9mEruWTF&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1iLogtw6dKQ">在<em>Starfield</em></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/forza-motorsport-wants-you-to-drive-forever-183033371.html"><em>Forza Motorsport</em></a>之前购买 Xbox Series X <em>&nbsp;</em>请注意，Verizon 正在出售<a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Verizon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2225d53b-bfe1-4d56-bd6e-3885c642b140&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Verizon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAV30_0N3PybdPvsjnA1rcakxFObDChMXScFBSBKnZj9z&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verizon.com%2Fproducts%2Fxbox-series-x-plus-free-robot-white-controller-bundle%2F">带有第二个控制器的 500 美元控制台，</a>无需额外付费。这并不是什么疯狂的事情，但备用的 Xbox 控制器通常售价 50 美元左右，而且 Series X 的任何形式的折扣都很少。事实上，微软本周表示，将于 8 月 1 日起在全球大部分地区<a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-is-increasing-xbox-series-x-and-game-pass-prices-in-most-countries-182635680.html"><em>提高</em>该游戏机的价格。</a>对于那些不关心顶级硬件的人来说，300 美元的<a data-i13n="cpos:63;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Xbox;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5f41950e-8ca3-4481-8466-a22b28b80e32&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Xbox&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI1ZjQxOTUwZS04Y2EzLTQ0ODEtODQ2Ni1hMjJiMjhiODBlMzIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueGJveC5jb20vZW4tVVMvY29uc29sZXMveGJveC1zZXJpZXMtcyNwdXJjaGFzZSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzkxN2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAV5OM5pCKwQDXJhuRtWzBYhco99g99UINNDV1emoTydi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fen-US%2Fconsoles%2Fxbox-series-s%23purchase">Xbox Series S</a>仍然具有很高的价值。 ，但如果您需要光盘驱动器和更稳定的性能，Series X 是您的最佳选择。</p><h2>三星 QN90B 55 英寸 4K 电视</h2><p><core-commerce id="11dc40472642454e83ce57a9ed3659e4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>我们的<a data-i13n="cpos:65;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-tvs-for-gaming-180033983.html">游戏电视购买指南</a>推荐的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:64;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbXAuJcKxA38d3gmb9vcnd20Jh52enmpmg2Zgmzz5XcT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09SBHSNNZ%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1" class="rapid-with-clickid">三星 QN90B</a> 55 英寸版本已降至 998 美元。这是历史新低。大多数评论表示，由于采用 Mini LED 背光，这款电视可为光线充足的房间提供足够的亮度，与大多数非 OLED 电视相比，具有流畅的运动性能和更丰富的对比度。它还具有四个完整的 HDMI 2.1 端口，可以播放高达 120 Hz 的 4K 内容。它仍然无法与优质 OLED 电视的对比度、响应时间或视角相媲美，但它应该更适合受眩光困扰的房间。然而，与大多数三星电视一样，它不支持杜比视界 HDR。三星已用<a data-i13n="cpos:66;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQlRUVkw0MTk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYY0-v-7BpJ80AHDhOfZpIYC2NtEvwBGcRoIPAOpR_as&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BTTVL419">新的 QN90C</a>取代了这款 2022 年型号，但该套件的 55 英寸版本目前价格高出 600 美元，因此 QN90B 暂时仍然具有更高的价值。</p><h2>三星 Galaxy Watch 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="82b39bb57d2e41dab1c787229046a5f2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:67;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjVUQjNRP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE0YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzkxN2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWiQntQfuL-DpTNEDx9m5QPh_cN-L6WPbhTNq0SxIGRo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J5TB3Q">三星 Galaxy Watch 5</a> 40 毫米型号降至 229 美元， <a data-i13n="cpos:68;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjRXNVRUP3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAU1TmQmGcWLZhjXtQLGpqR2ggaG5X4r_eZuqNKt3fF-7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J4W5TT%3Fth%3D1">44 毫米型号</a>降至 259 美元。这两笔交易均创下历史新低，但均距迄今为止的最佳价格不到 10 美元。去年我们给 Galaxy Watch 5 <a data-i13n="cpos:69;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-5-pro-review-battery-life-specs-durability-180052187.html">的评分为 85 分</a>，目前它是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:70;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">智能手表购买指南</a>中“最适合 Android 用户”的选择。虽然它的电池寿命可能会更长，但它的设计耐用且有吸引力，它的操作系统易于导航，而且它的健康跟踪相对全面。不过，三星预计将在未来几周内发布<a data-i13n="cpos:71;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-6-leak-suggests-the-rotating-bezel-will-return-124637657.html">Galaxy Watch 6</a> ，因此，如果您现在不需要新的智能手表，那么可能值得等待，看看该型号的表现如何。</p><p><strong><em>您的 Prime 会员日购物指南：</em></strong><em>查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:72;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报